title: Ep 32 - Let Go of The Past & Create The Future You Desire
itunes:title: Ep 32 - Let Go of The Past & Create The Future You Desire
description:
In order to create the future we desire we must first let go of the things in the past that may be holding us back. Hanging on to old memories or failures is like keeping an anchor attached to your sailboat as you sail away, you won't go anywhere. In this episode we talk about why it is so hard to let go and move on and also give three easy steps that make it easier to let go.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
